text: I had an amazing time at MusicBox Family Karaoke! They have a wide range of songs to choose from, and the sound system is absolutely top-notch. The rooms are clean and comfortable, making it the perfect spot for a fun night out. Highly recommend!
And again music box never disappointed me...the sound was nice and food really good..will recommend to my friends..thumbs up....

If you are crazy about karaoke then you should go here. The sound system is good but just two comments, you guys should add more song choices especially Indonesian songs hehe. And also the Aircond is a bittttt hot. The atmosphere is good for families so it is recommended if you want to bring your kids. They also have food and drinks here.

My son's favorite place.
Everything is perfect
